{"id":"b22b3c58-50d8-43c4-b888-e0f263c47b71","name":"Dragonball GT S.H. Figuarts Action Figure Super Saiyan 4 Son Goku 15cm","slug":"dragonball-gt-s.h.-figuarts-action-figur","description":"<p><b>Dragonball GT </b>action figure of <b>Super Saiyan 4 Son Goku </b>in <strong>S.H. Figuarts </strong>collection, size approx.15 cm, <b>official product</b> by <strong>Tamashii Nations</strong>.</p>\n<p>For the first time in <strong>S.H.Figuarts</strong>, here is <strong>Goku</strong> <strong>Super Saiyan 4</strong> from <strong>Dragon Ball GT</strong>.</p>\n<p>In <strong>Dragon Ball GT</strong>, it was <strong>Son Goku</strong> who was the first to have the honor of taking advantage of the immense powers of this form of <strong>Super Saiyan 4</strong> during his fight against <strong>Baby Vegeta</strong>. In this form, <strong>Super Saiyans</strong>' hair becomes longer and thicker. The body is then covered with thick red fur as well as on the tail, the eyes are also circled in red. This transformation is considered the most powerful of all.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><strong>Content :</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Interchangeable faces</li>\n<li>Interchangeable hands</li>\n<li>Kamehameha effect</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This product is not a toy or product for children. It is a collectors item intended for adults only.</p>","metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":null,"model":null,"releaseDate":null,"image":null,"condition":null,"edition":null,"rarity":null,"features":null,"specifications":null,"createdAt":"2025-03-25T23:56:42.991Z","updatedAt":"2025-03-25T23:56:42.991Z","barcode":"4573102608697","deletedAt":null,"brandId":"3973100e-a304-42f2-b48a-5e810adf1082","franchiseId":null,"seriesId":null,"lineId":null,"categories":[{"productId":"b22b3c58-50d8-43c4-b888-e0f263c47b71","categoryId":"bc7dcae3-c133-443f-85e0-737ca2ab3570","category":{"id":"bc7dcae3-c133-443f-85e0-737ca2ab3570","name":"Collectibles","slug":"collectibles","description":"Auto-imported category: Co